.RE
.PP
\fBReturns:\fP
.RS 4
An hx509 error code, see \fBhx509_get_error_string()\fP. 
.RE
.PP

.SS "int hx509_crl_sign (hx509_context context, hx509_cert signer, hx509_crl crl, heim_octet_string * os)"
