.PP
\fBParameters:\fP
.RS 4
\fIcontext\fP a hx509 context. 
.br
\fIsigner\fP certificate to sign the CRL with 
.br
\fIcrl\fP the CRL to sign 
.br
\fIos\fP return the signed and encoded CRL, free with free_heim_octet_string()
.RE
.PP
\fBReturns:\fP
.RS 4
